Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Question}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.36,0:00:04.73,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Alola!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.73,0:00:07.99,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I, Mao, will give today’s problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.99,0:00:13.16,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Which of these Pokémon \N does Satoshi catch today?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.16,0:00:15.50,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Get the answer at the end of the episode!
Comment: 10,0:00:15.50,0:00:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Prologue}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.50,0:00:22.25,Main,Moani,0,0,0,,Here you go, little Nyabi{honorific note: Nyabi-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.34,0:00:27.88,Main,Moani,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.64,0:00:34.01,Main,Moani,0,0,0,,It’s a flock of Tsutsukera!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.39,Main,Moani,0,0,0,,It’s that time again already?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.74,0:00:53.41,Main,Moani,0,0,0,,It’s quite all right. \N They only come here at this time of year.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.99,0:00:58.91,Main,Moani,0,0,0,,The blessings of nature \N are to be shared equally between all. {Moani dabbing on the capitalist boomers FTW! - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.91,0:01:02.83,Main,Moani,0,0,0,,That’s the law for \N those who live in Alola.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.72,Main,Moani,0,0,0,,So feel free to come here \N whenever you feel hungry, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.80,0:01:19.68,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Satoshi and Pikachu are trying to catch \N their first Pokémon in the Alola Region.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.68,0:01:23.23,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,They are right in the middle of \N a Pokémon Battle as we speak!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.23,0:01:26.07,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Agojimushi. Larva Pokémon. \N Bug type.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.07,0:01:29.57,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Its strong jaw enables it to \N scrape trees and slurp out the sap.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.57,0:01:32.03,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It normally lives underground.{Sun Pokédex entry -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.57,0:01:34.70,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Satoshi! \N Did you get that-roto?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.70,0:01:36.41,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Sure did! \N Thanks, Rotom!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.87,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu, jump!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.08,0:01:41.91,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.84,0:01:55.80,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,To catch wild Pokémon, you first have to wear them out \N in a battle before throwing the Monster Ball.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.10,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,That’s a basic of \N Pokémon Battling-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.97,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right!
Comment: 10,0:02:08.48,0:02:08.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 10,0:03:36.49,0:03:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.34,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Will he manage to get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.26,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,He can do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.43,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.10,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,You almost had it...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.44,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.44,0:04:15.23,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,When Agojimushi comes out, \N you hit it with Lightning Speed!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.66,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Y-You’re such a scaredy-cat... {Hyphenated for consistency with other uses of “scaredy-cat”. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.25,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I-I-I most certainly am not!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.62,0:04:30.08,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I love Pokémon, \N as a subject to learn about! {Note that she said the same thing in episode 1, so... consistency. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.09,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.09,0:04:37.63,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Beware its sturdy jaw-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.01,0:04:45.72,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.73,0:04:51.06,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Damage confirmed! \N Damage confirmed on Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.48,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.61,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’ll show you to \N the Pokémon Center.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.07,0:05:00.66,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,There’s a Pokémon Center here? \N That’s great! Please do, Mao!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.37,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Lilie, don’t worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.20,0:05:08.12,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Satoshi, we’ll go back to the School \N and explain the situation to Professor Kukui.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.37,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kaki!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.14,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,This time, for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.14,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,C’mon, Mimikkyu!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.14,0:05:30.02,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} offered to help us out, \N so let me catch you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.77,0:05:35.11,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,It hasn’t been weakened at all, \N so of course it’d be hard to catch, meow.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.82,0:05:42.28,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,I’m trying to catch Mimikkyu because none of you \N can stand up to that Kiteruguma, remember?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.91,0:05:47.91,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,If we don’t get out of here already, \N we’ll be that thing’s dinner before long!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.37,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,Its... dinner?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.37,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,A Gorgeous Ball?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.42,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.17,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,D-Don’t!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.34,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,It’s a valuable part \N of my collection... {Ultra nitpick, but suggesting “part” in place of “piece”. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.76,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Collection?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.84,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,You know, Monster Balls are worthless \N if you don’t {\i1}use{\i0} them!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.55,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,Wait! Please! \N Do anything but—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.47,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Oh, sheesh, be quiet already!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.60,Main,Team Rocket,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.11,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,It went in!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.11,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.65,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,You got Mimikkyu, meow!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.49,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,That ball was meant \N for my collection!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.08,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.34,0:06:41.30,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,Kiteruguma’s saying \N it’s dinner time, meow!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.76,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.76,0:06:45.64,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Mimikkyu! Save us!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.64,0:06:49.43,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Mimikkyu! {\i1}Mimikkyu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.89,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.56,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,It’s so sweet! Delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.77,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,I’m filled with energy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.77,0:07:00.11,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,check,Th-This is Mitsuhoney honey, meow!{In hindsight, I’m not sure about simplifying “Mitsuhoney no Honeymitsu” like this. -TLC}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.94,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,It’s so sweet, meow!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.32,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,You’re right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.62,0:07:15.08,Main,Team Rocket,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is really nice \N somehow, isn’t it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.04,Main,Joy,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Melemele Island \N Pokémon Center!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.05,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Please take care of him, \N Ms. Joy{honorific note: Joy-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.84,0:07:28.93,Main,Joy,0,0,0,,Don’t worry. \N Your Pikachu will be better in no time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.26,Main,Joy,0,0,0,,Happinus, if you please...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.26,0:07:38.48,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,The Pokémon Center is a place where Pokémon can \N recover their health and be treated for any ailments-roto.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.44,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Ms. Joy{honorific note: Joy-san}. Updated.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.48,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Information updated.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.24,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Say, Rotom, who’s that Pokémon?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.99,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Roger that! Leave it to me-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.57,0:07:50.74,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Cuwawa. Posy Picker Pokémon. \N Fairy type.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.25,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It releases a soothing aroma \N from the flowers it’s plucked,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.25,0:07:57.96,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,which heals the stamina and ailments \N of both itself and other Pokémon.{This does not match its game dex entries. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.88,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It’s the perfect Pokémon to be \N Ms. Joy{honorific note: Joy-san}’s assistant!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.55,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Happinus is perfect for her, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.26,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,An accurate assessment-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.72,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Happinus. Happiness Pokémon. \N Normal type.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.18,0:08:13.51,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,When Happinus senses sadness \N with its fluffy coat of fur,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.51,0:08:18.14,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,it will rush over, no matter the distance, \N to share a Lucky Egg that brings a smile to any face.{Reworded from its ORAS Pokédex entry. What they had was just and simply too wordy. -Starfish}{Do we want to keep Lucky Egg? しあわせたまご - Literally “Happiness Egg”. -TLC}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.53,Main,Joy,0,0,0,,We’ve restored your Pikachu \N to full health.{Copied this straight from 104. Yay, script search! -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.45,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.24,0:08:32.16,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,That’s great, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.79,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Testing-roto...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.79,0:08:39.29,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Full health restoration \N confirmed-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.38,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Today is the day...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.72,0:09:35.51,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’m 100% gonna catch \N a Pokémon today!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.31,0:09:42.56,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,The forest behind the Pokémon School \N currently has an 89% chance of Pokémon appearing!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.61,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,That could be good!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.69,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I met Amakaji in that forest, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.01,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Wh-What Pokémon is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.01,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Leave it to me-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.01,0:10:21.23,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Mokuroh. Grass Feather Pokémon. \N Grass/Flying type.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.98,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It stores up energy during the day \N using photosynthesis.{This is IN its Sun Pokédex entry, but the exact phrasing doesn’t quite match. The next two lines are straight out of Moon. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.98,0:10:27.27,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Silently it glides, drawing near its targets.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.19,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Unnoticed, it starts pelting them \N with vicious kicks.{The game text is “Before they even notice it, it begins to pelt them with vicious kicks.” but that’s a BIT too much text for such a quick line. Honestly even this rewording is a bit excessive. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.49,0:10:36.62,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Not only was it noticed by its target, \N but it utterly failed to pelt it with vicious kicks...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.62,0:10:39.70,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Quite the contrary, \N it {\i1}took{\i0} a vicious attack-roto...{Oh and for the record... I’m going by the logic that since none of the characters KNOW Grass Owl yet, they also would not have noticed that he is a he. So... The dreaded “it” is acceptable in this episode. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.75,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Amakaji is used to this, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.96,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Used to it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.17,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,You see, Amakaji’s scent—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.50,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Leave the rest of that explanation \N to me-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.34,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Amakaji. Fruit Pokémon. \N Grass type.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.42,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,A delectable aroma pours from its body.{Sun Pokédex entry -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.59,0:11:00.06,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,There are many bird Pokémon who are \N lured in by this aroma, mistaking it for an actual fruit.{Kinda-sorta its Moon entry but not really. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.85,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Wait! Here it comes again-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.73,0:11:11.73,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It might be {\i1}really{\i0} hungry...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.67,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.34,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,That’s good!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.06,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,What an appetite!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.90,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It’s consuming a frightening amount \N at an alarming speed-roto...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.77,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Want this, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.82,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.78,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It’s got really strong legs!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.83,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Was it good?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.91,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I see. Glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.21,0:12:09.12,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,So soft!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.71,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Say, Mokuroh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.59,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I catch you...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.01,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.30,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Will you catch it-roto?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.30,0:12:22.97,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.89,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.35,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Roger that-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.77,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Pocket Monsters-roto!
Comment: 10,0:12:32.48,0:12:32.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.48,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll get Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.37,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,The coast is clear! \N We can get away now!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.37,0:12:49.75,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,I’ve got the Gorgeous Ball \N Mimikkyu went into!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.75,0:12:53.46,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,And my belly’s full, \N thanks to Kiteruguma, meow!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.80,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey, w-what are you...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.18,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Those jerks!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.10,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,They took Kiteruguma’s \N stockpile of food!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.02,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,What a bunch of villains!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.06,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,We’re getting it back!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.06,0:13:14.65,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.86,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,We owe Kiteruguma a debt for \N the lodging and food!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.86,0:13:20.86,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,If we ignore these jerks here, \N it would go against our path of righteous evil!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.99,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.95,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,Musashi’s so manly, meow! {Suggesting “Musashi’s so manly, meow!” Would love to suggest “Musashi’s so ballsy, meow!”, but family-friendly TV and all. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.49,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.29,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It’s my turn-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.45,0:14:14.58,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Tsutsukera. Woodpecker Pokémon. \N Normal/Flying type.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.46,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It can peck at a rate of 16 times a second \N to drill holes in trees.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.17,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It uses the holes for \N food storage and for nesting.{Sun Pokédex entry -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.88,0:14:26.01,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Kerarappa. Bugle Beak Pokémon. \N Tsutsukera’s evolved form.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.14,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It eats berries and \N stores their seeds in its beak.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.14,0:14:30.43,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,When it encounters enemies or prey, \N it fires off all the seeds in a burst.{Sun Pokédex entry -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.27,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Dodekabashi. Cannon Pokémon. \N Kerarappa’s evolved form.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.27,0:14:41.94,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,The temperature of its heated beak can exceed \N 100 degrees, causing severe burns when it hits.{Slight rewording of its Sun Pokédex entry -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.95,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Oh? It’s not warm at all-roto.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.95,0:14:48.87,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,How odd! This contradicts \N my explanation-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.58,0:14:56.00,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You had this many friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.46,0:15:02.71,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.68,0:15:08.47,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,When asked “Wh-What?!”...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.31,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,Let us tell you our names!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.31,0:15:14.23,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Flower’s face, willow’s waist, \N moon and flowers hide in her wake.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.23,0:15:17.27,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,A single flower of evil in this fleeting world!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.73,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.40,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,Nobility and elegance like \N a dragon dancing in the clouds.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.61,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,The apostle of darkness fighting back \N against a tragic world!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.24,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,Kojirou!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.24,0:15:28.95,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,It’s all for one and one for all!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.95,0:15:32.41,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,Even in close friendships, \N an evil star shines with a golden glow!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.29,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,Nyarth!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.42,Main,Team Rocket,0,0,0,,Team Rocket is here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.54,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.96,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,It’s you people from yesterday!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.17,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Team Rocket! \N Let the Tsutsukera go!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.55,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Not gonna happen, \N brat boy!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.93,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,These jerks stole \N Kiteruguma’s food!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.81,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,We will take it back, to show our gratitude \N for the lodging and food!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.27,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,Fire, meow!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.56,0:16:03.94,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,And then we’re giving Pikachu to Sakaki{honorific note: Sakaki-sama} \N as a present, too, while we’re at it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.15,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Mimikkyu! It’s all on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.74,0:16:13.08,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Mimikkyu, pummel them! \N I don’t even care how you do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.04,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,A Shadow Ball, meow!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.92,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu! Electric Ball!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.42,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mokuroh, now’s your chance! \N Go save your friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.43,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Use Iron Tail, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.94,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It broke through that net \N with a single kick-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.82,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,When...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.82,0:16:48.36,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,One of their friends, meow?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.32,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Mimikkyu! Attack again!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.91,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,That’s Mimikkyu’s \N Play Rough, meow!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.71,0:17:01.29,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.75,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Mimikkyu, finish them off!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.59,Main,Nyarth,0,0,0,,That’s Shadow Claw, meow!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.22,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,It can even use Shadow Claw?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.47,0:17:12.51,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Dodge it, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.98,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,That move... It’s Leafage!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.61,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Well done, Mokuroh!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.03,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu, are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.99,0:17:32.70,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Right! Use 100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.42,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Mimikkyu!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.23,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Is this what they call...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.86,Main,Kojiro,0,0,0,,...déjà vu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.65,Main,Team Rocket,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} Kiteruguma!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.69,0:18:12.36,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.36,0:18:16.70,Main,Musashi,0,0,0,,We were trying to repay our debt \N for the lodging and food!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.70,0:18:19.12,Main,Team Rocket,0,0,0,,What even {\i1}is{\i0} this feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.38,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,They’re off...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.38,0:18:26.50,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.23,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mokuroh looks happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.23,0:18:43.64,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.48,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mokuroh.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.24,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thank you. Everyone’s safe, \N thanks to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.20,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,That was a vicious kick-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.13,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.63,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go home, \N Pikachu, Rotom.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.63,0:19:15.34,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Go home? Weren’t you \N going to catch Mokuroh-roto?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.26,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It’s fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.80,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.14,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Does not compute. \N Does not compute.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.39,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.35,0:19:25.31,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mokuroh’s got all of \N these friends here!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.65,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,They’re family.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.70,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,So, it’s fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.22,0:20:02.10,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mokuroh! Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.65,0:20:10.81,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mokuroh...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.07,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You mean you want...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.86,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,...to come with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.07,0:20:19.36,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Roto?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.37,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.70,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I wanted to be with you, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.50,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mokuroh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.33,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,What’s it doing-roto?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.42,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Isn’t it obvious?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.88,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You’re telling me \N to catch you, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.51,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right! Let’s go, Mokuroh!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.43,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Here’s the Monster Ball!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.86,0:20:56.78,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I got Mokuroh!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.61,0:21:02.03,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,I-It’s possible to catch \N a Pokémon like {\i1}that{\i0}-roto?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.03,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.87,0:21:08.21,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that’s just \N Satoshi’s style!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.71,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right, Mokuroh... \N Come out!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.23,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You really like my backpack, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.44,0:21:34.19,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Some Mokuroh love backpacks...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.44,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Data updated-roto...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.74,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,His first new Pokémon \N in the Alola Region...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.58,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,A carefree glutton...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.58,0:21:49.16,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Yet someone who can display \N tremendous power to protect its friends...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.75,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Satoshi has caught Mokuroh!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.75,0:21:55.46,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,With a new friend by his side, \N his adventure in Alola...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.46,0:21:58.05,Main,Narrator,450,0,0,,...has only just begun!
Comment: 10,0:21:59.46,0:21:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 10,0:23:20.50,0:23:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Answer}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.51,0:23:25.55,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.55,0:23:29.10,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,The answer to the PokéProblem \N was Mokuroh!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.10,0:23:33.64,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,The Grass Feather Pokémon Mokuroh \N has strong legs and is great at kicking!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.64,0:23:37.10,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Even its Tackle attack uses its legs!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.10,0:23:40.61,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, and it seems like Mokuroh really likes Satoshi’s backpack.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.61,0:23:44.36,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,It looks really cute \N peeking out from there, doesn’t it?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.53,0:23:48.32,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mokuroh’s asleep again...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.96,0:23:59.58,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Comment: 10,0:24:00.46,0:24:00.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.25,0:24:03.09,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Today’s class is on fishing!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.09,0:24:04.84,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,I’ll be the teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.84,0:24:06.17,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.17,0:24:08.43,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Suiren’s great at fishing, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.43,0:24:11.30,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,All right, do as I tell you.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.06,0:24:15.35,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, you can even fish up \N the Legendary Pokémon Kaiogre here!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.35,0:24:16.81,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.81,0:24:20.73,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go, you guys! \N We’re gonna get that Kaiogre, for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.73,0:24:23.86,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Come on, Suiren... \N The boys are actually serious about this!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.86,0:24:26.65,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Next time, on Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.65,0:24:28.91,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Ashimari, Do Your Balloon-est!
