Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.48,0:02:15.11,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}“I’m Satoshi from Masara Town! My dream is to be a Pokémon Master!”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:15.11,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}“I’m Satoshi from Masara Town! My dream is to be a Pokémon Master!”
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.12,OP,,0,0,0,,“This is my partner, Pikachu!”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.12,OPp2,,0,0,0,,“This is my partner, Pikachu!”
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.12,0:02:23.33,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}“Let’s all search for Pokémon together, at full power!”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:23.33,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}“Let’s all search for Pokémon together, at full power!”
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.09,0:02:30.09,OP,,0,0,0,,Just standing around waiting won’t get us anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:30.09,OPp2,,0,0,0,,Just standing around waiting won’t get us anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.09,0:02:33.47,OP,,0,0,0,,I want to go on a grand adventure that’ll make
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:33.47,OPp2,,0,0,0,,I want to go on a grand adventure that’ll make
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.47,0:02:38.26,OP,,0,0,0,,the sun, the moon, the Pokémon, and that girl all turn to look in awe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:38.26,OPp2,,0,0,0,,the sun, the moon, the Pokémon, and that girl all turn to look in awe
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.01,OP,,0,0,0,,(Ay-ya-ya!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.01,OPp2,,0,0,0,,(Ay-ya-ya!)
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.56,OP,,0,0,0,,It’s a thrilling, surprising, astonishing, naturally endless journey
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.56,OPp2,,0,0,0,,It’s a thrilling, surprising, astonishing, naturally endless journey
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.81,OP,,0,0,0,,Things to find here and there and everywhere, it’s almost too much
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.81,OPp2,,0,0,0,,Things to find here and there and everywhere, it’s almost too much
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.81,0:02:50.61,OP,,0,0,0,,Now let’s keep going on and on and on and on and on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:50.61,OPp2,,0,0,0,,Now let’s keep going on and on and on and on and on!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.57,OP,,0,0,0,,(Ay-ya-ya!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.57,OPp2,,0,0,0,,(Ay-ya-ya!)
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.57,0:02:58.83,OP,,0,0,0,,For heated battles, I choose you! (For heated battles, I choose you!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:58.83,OPp2,,0,0,0,,For heated battles, I choose you! (For heated battles, I choose you!)
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.83,0:03:06.08,OP,,0,0,0,,Now, let’s finish it! I got you! (Now, let’s finish it! I got you!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:06.08,OPp2,,0,0,0,,Now, let’s finish it! I got you! (Now, let’s finish it! I got you!)
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.21,OP,,0,0,0,,(Go!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.21,OPp2,,0,0,0,,(Go!)
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.21,0:03:14.67,OP,,0,0,0,,Sun, sun, burn hotter! Break into a sprint with your blazing heartbeat! (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:14.67,OPp2,,0,0,0,,Sun, sun, burn hotter! Break into a sprint with your blazing heartbeat! (Yeah!)
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.67,0:03:22.18,OP,,0,0,0,,Moon, moon, your overflowing courage will brighten our dreams! (Ay-ya-ya!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:22.18,OPp2,,0,0,0,,Moon, moon, your overflowing courage will brighten our dreams! (Ay-ya-ya!)
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.18,0:03:27.19,OP,,0,0,0,,With your full body and soul, give it all you’ve got
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:27.19,OPp2,,0,0,0,,With your full body and soul, give it all you’ve got
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.19,0:03:30.44,OP,,0,0,0,,and shout it out loud: “Alola”!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:30.44,OPp2,,0,0,0,,and shout it out loud: “Alola”!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:33.44,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{=3}
Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{=4}ENDING
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:07.10,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Yo! Champ in the making! Now, let’s keep up the enthusiasm today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:10.81,OPED,,0,0,0,,Get them, get them! (Get them, get them!) Now, let’s keep making friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:12.35,OPED,,0,0,0,,No Super Ball, Hyper Ball, or even a Master Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:14.56,OPED,,0,0,0,,can capture your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:18.23,OPED,,0,0,0,,But if we dance together, things’ll keep getting more lively!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:22.11,OPED,,0,0,0,,Normal, Fighting, Poison, Ground, Flying, Bug, Rock, Ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:23.99,OPED,,0,0,0,,Steel, Fire, Water, Electric, Grass, Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:25.91,OPED,,0,0,0,,Esper, Dragon, Evil, Fairy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:29.54,OPED,,0,0,0,,Whether they’re evolved or not, get them all together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:33.29,OPED,,0,0,0,,and strike a full power pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.13,OPED,,0,0,0,,Blazing, crackling Fire fires you up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:40.80,OPED,,0,0,0,,An Electric shock makes you tremble
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:44.47,OPED,,0,0,0,,A Ghost looms over you, cackling ominously
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:48.47,OPED,,0,0,0,,The world’s greatest Fighting men go Ka-thwack! Ka-thwack! Ka-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:55.90,OPED,,0,0,0,,I’m glad I met you, I’m really glad I chose you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:23:03.32,OPED,,0,0,0,,Once we’ve stuffed plenty of memories into our pockets
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:10.87,OPED,,0,0,0,,Let’s walk while holding hands, and stay together even through painful times
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:20.50,OPED,,0,0,0,,So that we can meet here again once we’ve grown up
Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{=5}
